==Latin==
===Adjective Suffix===
'''-alis'''

Third declension

# Suffix added to various forms of words to create adjectives.  See also ''[[-aris]].

: If the root word ends in ''-l'' or ''-lis'', Latin generally used ''[[-aris]]'' instead.  Sometimes both forms are found; e.g., ''[[linealis]]'' and ''[[linearis]]''.

